<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Makeaway</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="A personal field guide for building a freer life through hiking, side projects, money, travel, and figuring things out along the way."
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <main>
      <p class="eyebrow">Makeaway</p>

      <h1>A personal field guide for building a freer life.</h1>

      <p class="intro">
        Notes on hiking, escaping the rat race, side projects, money, travel,
        and figuring things out along the way.
      </p>

      <section class="cards">
        <article>
          <h2>Escape</h2>
          <p>Thoughts on work, burnout, freedom, and designing a life that feels more your own.</p>
        </article>

        <article>
          <h2>Outside</h2>
          <p>Hiking, camping, nature, gear, and the places that reset your brain.</p>
        </article>

        <article>
          <h2>Build</h2>
          <p>Side projects, websites, experiments, and learning new skills by actually making things.</p>
        </article>

        <article>
          <h2>Money</h2>
          <p>Investing, dividends, options, and the long road toward more independence.</p>
        </article>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  :root {
    font-family:
      Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI",
      sans-serif;
    color: #f5f1e8;
    background: #172117;
  }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    min-height: 100vh;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(144, 173, 110, 0.25), transparent 35%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, #111811, #26351f);
  }

  main {
    width: min(980px, calc(100% - 40px));
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 96px 0;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    color: #c9d8a6;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h1 {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6.5rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.06em;
  }

  .intro {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 28px 0 0;
    color: #ded8c8;
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 2vw, 1.45rem);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 18px;
    margin-top: 72px;
  }

  article {
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 241, 232, 0.18);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 24px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  article h2 {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  article p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #d5ccb8;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    main {
      padding: 64px 0;
    }

    .cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      margin-top: 48px;
    }
  }
</style>